| Statement     | Purpose                        |
| ------------- | ------------------------------ |
| `break`       | Exit current loop/switch early |
| `continue`    | Skip to next iteration         |
| `fallthrough` | Continue to next `switch` case |
| `return`      | Exit from function             |


